Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.00,0:00:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我是怜子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.17,0:00:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,34岁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.67,0:00:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,结婚7年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,丈夫多在海外出差
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我和管家生活在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.62,0:00:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,4姊妹的长女的我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,从小就很顽皮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.49,0:00:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,每天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.86,0:00:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,都会戏弄管家来排解无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.87,0:00:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,今天就让你们稍微见识一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.14,0:00:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,(小早川怜子)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.04,0:01:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,(贵妇优雅的肉棒玩弄消遣)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.39,0:01:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,首先来说说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.13,0:01:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,工作了3年的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.43,0:01:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,高桥君的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.23,0:01:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我的恶作剧现在才要开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.71,0:01:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,要说几次才会懂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不是说过我只用丝绸雯毛巾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉 怜子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.76,0:01:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不惩罚你不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:01:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,下次会注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.11,0:02:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.11,0:02:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.68,0:02:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,戴上这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.79,0:02:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.22,0:02:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 我下次会小心一点的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.79,0:02:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.16,0:02:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,衣服要穿好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.63,0:02:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.97,0:02:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,转过去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.39,0:02:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:02:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒是不是变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:02:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.23,0:03:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.48,0:03:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就算被这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.79,0:03:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,也完全没感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事情被您亲人发现了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.53,0:03:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不是很不妙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.53,0:03:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我丈夫去出差不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.81,0:03:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头就这么有感觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.11,0:03:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,真是下流的身体呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.36,0:04:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.73,0:04:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,自己脱掉衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,脱掉让我看看乳头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你的乳头变成这样了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,坐在后面的沙发也可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.38,0:05:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,衣服要脱好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.75,0:05:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,对不超
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头这不是硬梆梆的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.61,0:05:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那么有感觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我都还没摸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴巴张那么开是想要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.99,0:05:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,怜子夫人的唾液之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,想要那么下流的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,可以唷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是这个嘴巴想要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我的唾夜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.29,0:06:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那把嘴巴张开一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.65,0:06:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,唾液感觉如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,很美味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.63,0:06:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.73,0:06:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,想要被我这样做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,从见到怜子夫人的第一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,就想被这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才一直故意搞砸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.92,0:07:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,对不超
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.32,0:07:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个人真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.87,0:07:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是唾液哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怜子夫人的唾液
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好美味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.28,0:07:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,变得硬邦邦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,已经变得这么大了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢被温柔地对待吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:07:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,更多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.53,0:08:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,捏激烈一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢被捏阿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,就像这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.04,0:08:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,只捏前端吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.88,0:08:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,身体抖抖的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,真是下流的乳头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,捏就可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.44,0:08:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,捏就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,想被咬吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,想要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.35,0:08:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那就咬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,另一边也
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,已经硬邦邦了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,身体抖抖的真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,想摸我身体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:09:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,想摸怜子夫人的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不慢慢地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,享受可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,想摸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.28,0:10:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.09,0:10:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,把双手举起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,太舒服了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,变得硬梆梆的了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.90,0:11:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.47,0:11:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,变得怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,变得硬梆梆的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.34,0:11:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那自己脱掉裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.30,0:11:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这么小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.53,0:11:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.47,0:12:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 怜子夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,想要我摸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,想要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.67,0:12:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,再好好地拜托我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,请摸我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.24,0:12:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那我帮你摸乳头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.41,0:12:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,下面也
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,下面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.85,0:12:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,变大了 在蠕动着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.26,0:12:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,娈得很有精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:13:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,原来你乳头那么有感觉阿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.87,0:13:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.81,0:13:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,两边同时被玩弄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这个肉棒想放进我里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,想和我故吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,想和怜子夫人做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.44,0:13:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能跟你做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这里这么小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.15,0:13:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.36,0:13:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,只是摸的话可以唷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.99,0:14:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,可以摸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不是是我来摸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我的唾液
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.68,0:14:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,涂了一堆在手上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.32,0:14:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,变得好有精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,想要故更舒服的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,想要吗 被我做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.81,0:14:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,被这样用的话 我要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真没出息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:14:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,澧样子就要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.88,0:15:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,还太早了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.59,0:15:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.35,0:15:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你做跟这犀牛一样的姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,犀牛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.03,0:15:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.20,0:15:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.67,0:15:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这个喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,做跟这犀牛一样的姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.61,0:15:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.41,0:15:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,在桌子上做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.08,0:15:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是 这样就
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.48,0:15:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头有感觉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.76,0:16:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,变得硬梆梆的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,只有前端
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.63,0:16:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢地摸前端吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,还是要快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.60,0:16:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不行唷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.37,0:16:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉好像流汗了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:17:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,欺负前端的话要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.24,0:17:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,只是用前端就要射了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不行唷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,还要尽情地玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.63,0:17:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,想摸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.17,0:17:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.88,0:17:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.65,0:17:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我脱掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.68,0:17:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,可以脱掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.59,0:18:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,想摸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.42,0:18:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,还不能摸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.13,0:19:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不变得再硬一点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,想要摩擦我的小穴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.38,0:19:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,想要再湿一点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,只有前端唷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.81,0:19:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,只有前端
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.98,0:19:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,里面也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,变得好热
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,有感觉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉快射了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.34,0:20:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那就前端
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,前端
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.78,0:20:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢往里面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.62,0:20:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,往里面摸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.79,0:20:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,变得好大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.84,0:20:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:20:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.51,0:21:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,接着来摩擦根部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.26,0:21:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,要停下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,怜子夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.28,0:21:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,想射在怜子夫人的脸或胸部上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.89,0:21:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那帮我脱掉胸罩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.76,0:21:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.36,0:21:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那么就失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.56,0:21:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,脱掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.63,0:21:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.17,0:21:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,脱掉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.43,0:22:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,想射在我的胸部上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.20,0:22:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.27,0:22:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,再靠近点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.92,0:22:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,用我的乳头
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.06,0:22:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,用乳头摩擦着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.73,0:22:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.65,0:23:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害 变得好红
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.09,0:23:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你想被这样做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.26,0:23:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.47,0:23:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不行不让你射
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,请让我射
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.71,0:23:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 我还想玩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.72,0:23:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,只用前端来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.50,0:24:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,请让我放进中间里面
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.23,0:24:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.78,0:24:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.74,0:24:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.48,0:24:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,可以唷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.15,0:24:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.72,0:24:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说想放进中间里面
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.12,0:24:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得哪个比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.16,0:24:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,请让我放进中间里面
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.39,0:24:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.10,0:24:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那么舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.40,0:24:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这里面
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.94,0:24:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,放进我中间里面很舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.21,0:24:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.08,0:24:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,请继续做
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.32,0:25:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,想被榨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.79,0:25:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,想
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.60,0:25:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,可以再继续榨我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.46,0:25:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.20,0:25:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,想被这样玩弄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.94,0:25:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.47,0:25:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,只有前端还是根部也
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.98,0:25:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.15,0:25:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,前端
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.08,0:25:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,变得好大
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.45,0:25:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真下流
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.25,0:25:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.89,0:25:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这边也变得好大
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.73,0:25:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,再让你变得更湿湿黏黏的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.77,0:25:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.77,0:25:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,唾液要流下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.95,0:26:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,湿湿黏黏的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.46,0:26:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,把舌头伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.90,0:26:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样子舔喔
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.90,0:26:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,要伸进来吗 把唾液用进来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.12,0:26:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好下流的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.99,0:26:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.23,0:26:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.20,0:26:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.44,0:26:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,已经
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.97,0:27:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,可以唷
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.04,0:27:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,可以唷
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.58,0:27:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,射出来
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.45,0:27:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.39,0:27:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.09,0:27:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不行我还要
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.92,0:27:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,想摩擦我的乳头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.66,0:27:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,请让我射 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.23,0:27:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.90,0:27:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,还想继续玩的说
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.71,0:27:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,可以唷
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.89,0:27:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,可以再继续榨我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.93,0:27:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.49,0:27:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.90,0:28:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.68,0:28:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,包起来
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.45,0:28:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,放进来
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.49,0:28:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,真任性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.17,0:28:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,可以唷
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.07,0:28:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.90,0:28:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.68,0:28:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.82,0:28:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,要停下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.26,0:29:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,可以就这样继续吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.09,0:29:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.13,0:29:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.73,0:29:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样继续下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.63,0:29:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,射了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.58,0:29:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.62,0:29:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.83,0:29:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.16,0:29:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好浓稠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.97,0:29:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.64,0:29:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,还能再射出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.18,0:29:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了 请原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.18,0:29:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,请原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.32,0:30:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 射不出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.30,0:30:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.90,0:30:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我找到新的兴趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.27,0:30:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,怜子夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.08,0:30:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.21,0:30:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我才要谢谢你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.39,0:30:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.56,0:30:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我从这天后
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.33,0:30:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,变成最喜欢被虐狂的男性了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.13,0:30:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,从那以后
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.77,0:30:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就只雇用被虐狂的管家的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.77,0:30:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,接着
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.21,0:30:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,来说我第一次和管家发生关系
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.91,0:31:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那天的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.52,0:31:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,或许是第一次感到自由的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.82,0:31:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,怜子夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.86,0:31:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.13,0:31:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.00,0:31:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这是这次的新作
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.70,0:31:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这次丈夫的出差
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.57,0:31:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不会太长了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.44,0:31:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,都将近一年没回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.75,0:31:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那会如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.45,0:31:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我是女性喔
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.19,0:31:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,很寂寞呀
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.86,0:31:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多可以让我做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.00,0:31:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,怜子夫人那是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.27,0:32:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我会被主人杀掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.77,0:32:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.31,0:32:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,想被开除吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.98,0:32:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那也不想怜子夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.82,0:32:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我还有家人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.35,0:32:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那你把衣服脱掉
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.19,0:32:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不 那种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.02,0:32:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那就把你开除吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.96,0:32:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是 我脱
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.36,0:32:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,快点脱掉
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.00,0:32:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.50,0:32:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就脱
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.20,0:32:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你不要开除我
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.81,0:32:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.86,0:32:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,脱好了话就坐到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.13,0:32:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.93,0:33:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,对 快点坐性爱
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.67,0:33:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.11,0:33:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 怜子夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.38,0:33:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,再下去我会背叛主人的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.99,0:33:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,和被我开除比
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.96,0:33:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,哪一边比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.60,0:33:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想被开除
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.10,0:33:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.43,0:33:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.77,0:33:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,怜子夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.61,0:33:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,请放过我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.58,0:33:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你不也很有精神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.38,0:33:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不 这个 不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.58,0:33:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这样子的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.45,0:33:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,说着 不是这样子的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.99,0:34:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,可是却立起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.33,0:34:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,怜子夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.84,0:34:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.17,0:34:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,让我满足吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.38,0:34:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,可以不要开除我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.38,0:34:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.05,0:34:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,能让我开心的话可以唷
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.32,0:34:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,因为不能由我主动来
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.79,0:34:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么都不用做
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.93,0:34:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么都不用做
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.53,0:34:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,保持这样就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.00,0:34:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,由我来做
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.43,0:34:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.48,0:34:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,没错你什么都不用做
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.35,0:35:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 把舌头伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.69,0:35:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.84,0:35:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么都不用做唷
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.48,0:35:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这个实在是
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.58,0:35:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这个不是很不妙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.55,0:35:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.09,0:35:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不那个
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.49,0:35:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能看到怜子夫人的裸体
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.56,0:35:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,才没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.34,0:36:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,怜子夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.22,0:36:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.02,0:36:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系唷 你什么都不用做
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.76,0:36:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,请绝对不要让主人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.23,0:36:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,可以唷
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.13,0:36:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.92,0:36:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.59,0:36:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.83,0:36:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.17,0:36:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,人的肌肤真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.04,0:37:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么都不用做
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.84,0:37:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.64,0:37:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这样不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.22,0:37:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,把舌头伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.62,0:37:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.33,0:37:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,把舌头伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.36,0:38:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.87,0:38:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 把舌头伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.57,0:38:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.51,0:38:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没错再来
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.78,0:38:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 忘记那个人的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.82,0:38:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.92,0:38:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.33,0:38:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,再多舔一点
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.13,0:38:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.04,0:38:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都不用做喔
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.24,0:38:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那里不行
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.64,0:38:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那里是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.91,0:38:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.25,0:38:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.52,0:38:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.19,0:38:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.26,0:39:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你就像舔冰淇淋一样舔就好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.06,0:39:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 那个我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.43,0:39:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都不能做
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.23,0:39:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不遵守也没关杰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.48,0:39:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.62,0:39:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那里 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.36,0:39:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里不行
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.79,0:39:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.39,0:39:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.36,0:39:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.36,0:39:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,和肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.04,0:39:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,想要摸到深处吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.54,0:39:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说只有前端
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.94,0:39:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不哪边都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.15,0:39:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,真可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.88,0:40:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.35,0:40:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,另一边也
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.53,0:40:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能主动做
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.56,0:40:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不做也没关系唷
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.21,0:40:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,躺在床上
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.18,0:40:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.02,0:40:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么都不用做
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.19,0:40:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,怜子夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.39,0:40:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那个不行
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.69,0:40:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我想干嘛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.29,0:40:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.76,0:40:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我会没有脸见主人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.54,0:41:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害 不能乱动喔
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.99,0:41:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.38,0:41:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.32,0:41:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,很不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.19,0:41:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,什么很不妙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.83,0:41:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,什么很不妙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.14,0:42:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,只有那里
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.18,0:42:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那里是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.28,0:42:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头 被摸的话
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.59,0:42:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.16,0:42:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来好好吃的乳头
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.76,0:42:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,忍不住好想摸
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.24,0:42:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那不摸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.78,0:42:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那里也
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.78,0:42:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.33,0:42:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,只有前端
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.60,0:43:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说根部也要
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.07,0:43:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说想要我的乳头
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.67,0:43:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,想要这样摩擦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.08,0:43:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,对我而言哪个都有点
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.95,0:43:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那你想要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.65,0:43:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.02,0:43:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.82,0:43:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,很害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.52,0:43:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.03,0:43:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,很害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.49,0:43:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,很害羞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.13,0:43:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.40,0:43:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.53,0:43:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害 弯过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.97,0:43:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,怜子夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.30,0:43:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这个样子很丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.57,0:43:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,还能再弯一点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.74,0:43:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,屁眼被看光了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.58,0:43:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,真下流在抽动着
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.01,0:43:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好去脸
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.98,0:43:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我最喜欢看别人丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.52,0:43:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,可以唷
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.15,0:43:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,弯的好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.66,0:44:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要拉的那么用力
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.99,0:44:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.93,0:44:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.33,0:44:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.21,0:44:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这么丢脸的姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.05,0:44:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我会没有脸见主人的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.43,0:44:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.37,0:44:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,什么不行
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.72,0:45:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的不行
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.49,0:45:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.17,0:45:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,看见你这个样子让我兴奋了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.82,0:45:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,想要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.99,0:45:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,想要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.99,0:45:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能说那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.86,0:45:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.50,0:45:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我也全部脱掉
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.31,0:45:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.01,0:45:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,怜子夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.64,0:45:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.78,0:46:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.06,0:46:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,想被胸部夹住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.79,0:46:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我快忍不住了 怜子夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.73,0:46:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.33,0:46:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,还可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.00,0:46:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真的到极限了 怜子夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.63,0:46:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不行再来
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.01,0:46:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.41,0:46:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,什么不行了会变怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.82,0:46:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,已经忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.69,0:46:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那就不要忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.82,0:46:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那么想要的话
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.09,0:46:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,就给你
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.03,0:47:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人真的不行
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.56,0:47:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不行不舔的话就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.24,0:48:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.75,0:48:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这样下去的话要忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.52,0:48:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那个真的不行
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.28,0:48:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 给我让开
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.02,0:48:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,怜子夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.06,0:48:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不能拒绝喔
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.16,0:48:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不想被开除吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.69,0:48:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.09,0:48:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这个硬梆梆的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.96,0:48:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,只有开除
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.50,0:48:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那个果然还是很不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.60,0:48:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,等等你在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.24,0:48:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.24,0:48:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,给我看清楚进去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.18,0:48:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,怜子夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.30,0:49:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们尽情地来品尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.70,0:49:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.00,0:49:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都不能做
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.87,0:49:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 没关系唷
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.71,0:49:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我会尽情地来品尝的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.46,0:49:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 那里
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.10,0:49:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.63,0:49:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴像那样子
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.97,0:49:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不行好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.20,0:50:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.37,0:50:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.34,0:50:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你就这样子就好
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.14,0:50:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么都不用做
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.15,0:50:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,看得到进去的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.99,0:50:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,很厉害 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.25,0:51:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 你就保持这样
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.28,0:51:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不要乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.08,0:51:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 不能乱动喔
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.74,0:51:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 不能摸那里
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.14,0:51:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我这个不行
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.21,0:51:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你露出了好棒的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.92,0:51:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.82,0:51:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,两边都
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.69,0:51:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.29,0:51:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.53,0:51:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你听我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.13,0:51:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,想要沾着口水弄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.10,0:51:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.77,0:51:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这么湿湿黏黏的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.51,0:52:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,想要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.22,0:52:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,放过我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.19,0:52:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.99,0:52:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.50,0:52:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,再让我开心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.45,0:52:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.75,0:52:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不那个
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.55,0:52:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.55,0:52:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.02,0:52:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.09,0:52:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没错再多做一点
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.76,0:52:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不由我来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.80,0:53:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系唷 不用装乖了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.14,0:53:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 不要乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.57,0:53:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,抱紧一点
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.04,0:53:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,让我受伤的话会出大事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.31,0:53:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.19,0:53:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,起鸡皮疙瘩了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.80,0:53:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.64,0:53:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.21,0:53:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,忍住还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.35,0:53:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么都不用做
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.75,0:53:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是我什么都不做
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.48,0:53:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.10,0:54:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是什么表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.31,0:54:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.27,0:54:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 前端 真的不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.14,0:54:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要用那里
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.75,0:54:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,怜子夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.69,0:54:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那个请饶过我
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.17,0:54:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.61,0:54:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.68,0:54:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不行好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.68,0:54:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.35,0:55:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.09,0:55:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.12,0:55:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我的忍耐也
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.26,0:55:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.09,0:55:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.93,0:55:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我的忍耐己经到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.51,0:55:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,极限
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.94,0:55:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我不懂这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.98,0:56:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,请理解
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.55,0:56:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.96,0:56:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.59,0:56:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.30,0:56:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.40,0:56:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真的不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.27,0:56:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.00,0:56:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.21,0:56:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.47,0:56:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.61,0:56:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.05,0:56:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.29,0:56:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.06,0:56:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.20,0:56:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是什么都没做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.60,0:56:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.64,0:56:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,有点不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.14,0:57:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,还这么有精神的说
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.87,0:57:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,还能射吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.91,0:57:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.21,0:57:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,真下流
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.05,0:57:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没有满足喔
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.32,0:57:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,还没我还要
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.79,0:57:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,让我满足吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.49,0:57:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 真的不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.09,0:57:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.90,0:57:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这个前端也想放进来
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.90,0:57:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.64,0:57:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.08,0:57:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.58,0:57:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不行我还要
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.09,0:57:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真的不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.80,0:58:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.20,0:58:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,什么哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.44,0:58:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.07,0:58:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里什么
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.45,0:58:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,再多取悦我一点
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.02,0:58:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,再让我满足一点
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.85,0:58:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.45,0:58:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.59,0:58:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,真的不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.34,0:58:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.94,0:58:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,真的不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.11,0:58:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 再来再取悦我一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.25,0:58:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这个角度 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.39,0:59:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然和他闹翻了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.29,0:59:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,到了现在也记得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.80,0:59:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他那挣扎的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.20,0:59:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.44,0:59:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,接着是
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.31,0:59:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,为了找到被虐狂的管家
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.74,0:59:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,面试
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.02,0:59:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是希望当管家的孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.95,0:59:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.22,0:59:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.93,0:59:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,有当过管家的经验吗
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.56,0:59:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.86,0:59:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,管家经验为3年
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.47,0:59:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然还不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.80,0:59:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.57,0:59:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真是可爱的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.34,0:59:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那么就
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.71,0:59:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,马上来开始考试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.08,0:59:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.71,0:59:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,首先把手伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.45,0:59:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没错把手伸到前面
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.55,1:00:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这固是
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.96,1:00:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,别问那么多
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.86,1:00:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,闭上嘴巴
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.16,1:00:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是考试
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.96,1:00:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,有这种考试吗
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.93,1:00:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,有哦
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.30,1:00:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这里的考试都是这样的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.57,1:00:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,加油合格吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.09,1:00:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,首先是
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.62,1:00:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,先躺下去
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.89,1:00:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,躺下去
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.26,1:00:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.66,1:00:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,还不快点做
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.46,1:00:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这个愚钝的像伙
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.96,1:00:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.30,1:00:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,对 把手举起来
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.34,1:00:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,把手放在头上
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.28,1:01:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.98,1:01:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.29,1:01:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,想成为我的管家吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.56,1:01:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.96,1:01:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那就必须乖乖接受考试
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.10,1:01:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉得到吗
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.01,1:01:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.44,1:01:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,什么不行
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.45,1:01:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉好痛苦的表情
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.76,1:01:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,很可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.83,1:01:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.14,1:01:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,怜子夫人 这个究竟是
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.04,1:02:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,考试喔
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.27,1:02:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是考试吗
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.51,1:02:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,想合格的话
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.15,1:02:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,就好好接受考试
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.65,1:02:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,再给我变得精神一点
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.85,1:02:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.68,1:02:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.95,1:02:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是硬梆梆了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.52,1:02:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系唷
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.96,1:02:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.97,1:03:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,什么的考试呢
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.67,1:03:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.65,1:03:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 想要我住手吗
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.42,1:03:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.15,1:03:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,要放弃考试吗
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.05,1:03:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.39,1:03:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,想要就这样继续下去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.49,1:03:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.21,1:03:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.78,1:03:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你变得硬梆梆的了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.78,1:03:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,变得这么硬
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.52,1:03:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛把嘴巴张那么开
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.82,1:03:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,想要吗
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.89,1:04:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那就给你吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.27,1:04:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你真可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.50,1:04:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴巴张那么开
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.41,1:04:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是还想要吗
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.01,1:04:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,想要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.14,1:04:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.68,1:04:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,可以唷
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.25,1:05:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然自己主动索求
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.02,1:05:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你真可爱
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.42,1:05:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,很痛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.33,1:05:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,可以唷
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.63,1:05:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.59,1:05:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这条裤子很碍眼呢
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.00,1:05:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,把它脱掉吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.57,1:05:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.04,1:05:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,再让我瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.91,1:06:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,其实
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.78,1:06:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让我直接摸吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.72,1:06:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这样子的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.86,1:06:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,很想要我脱掉内裤直接摸吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.83,1:06:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这么地有精神
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.28,1:06:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来把内裤脱掉
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.85,1:06:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.06,1:06:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,站到我的前面来
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.89,1:06:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好好地脱掉
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.80,1:06:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是变得很有精神了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.11,1:07:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真下流
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.87,1:07:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真可爱呢只用前端吗
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.71,1:07:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说想要单脚来摩擦呢
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.92,1:07:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,前端是只用这里的前端吗
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.22,1:07:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.79,1:07:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.86,1:07:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,什么不行
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.79,1:07:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,太激烈了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.43,1:07:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,什么很激烈
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.33,1:08:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,想要再温柔一点吗
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.83,1:08:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,想要温柔一点吗
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.00,1:08:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,再变得精神点
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.11,1:08:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.61,1:08:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.65,1:08:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,用我的屁股
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.32,1:08:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,自己来摩擦看看
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.33,1:08:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.39,1:08:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,把裙子掀起来
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.73,1:08:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.63,1:08:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没错就是这样
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.74,1:08:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,摩擦吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.84,1:08:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,用你的肉棒摩擦变得更有精神
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.08,1:08:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.06,1:08:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.96,1:09:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,再多摩擦一点
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.84,1:09:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,想放进我的里面吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.54,1:09:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.67,1:09:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,才不让你放进来呢
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.74,1:09:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,还不够
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.34,1:09:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不行唷
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.76,1:09:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,让你摩擦个够
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.17,1:09:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,可以唷 摩擦我的下面
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.97,1:09:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.91,1:09:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,再变得硬一点
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.72,1:10:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,变得越来越舒服了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.59,1:10:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,没错再来
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.70,1:10:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,直接
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.17,1:10:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,想直接接触吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.28,1:10:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.88,1:10:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那把我的丝袜
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.61,1:10:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,脱掉
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.69,1:10:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,用嘴巴脱喔
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.59,1:10:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,用嘴巴
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.86,1:10:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,用嘴巴
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.83,1:10:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,来 手也用上
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.36,1:10:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好好地脱掉
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.50,1:10:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.35,1:11:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,把它脱掉
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.79,1:11:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,用嘴巴脱掉
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.76,1:11:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.80,1:11:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我的小可爱
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.67,1:11:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,被我直接玩弄
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.34,1:11:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,来尽情地玩吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.12,1:11:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,想被缓慢地摸吗
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.76,1:11:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,想慢慢地来吗
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.19,1:11:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,请再多摸摸我
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.30,1:11:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,想被摸哪里
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.53,1:11:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.37,1:11:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,前端吗
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.83,1:11:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,还是全部
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.21,1:12:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说想被夹住
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.08,1:12:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,想被夹住
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.71,1:12:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那躺在下去
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.52,1:12:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,躺下去
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.15,1:12:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,再用我的脚尽情地夹住
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.04,1:12:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.91,1:12:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,很可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.35,1:12:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,想被尽情地摩擦吗
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.35,1:12:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么不行
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.79,1:12:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,其实很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.76,1:12:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这么有感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.90,1:13:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,想要吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.60,1:13:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.74,1:13:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,想要吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.79,1:13:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我的口水沾上去了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.32,1:13:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,变得湿湿黏黏的了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.13,1:13:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.66,1:13:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,请再给我多一点口水
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.86,1:13:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,真可爱还 想要吗
